    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Booking
    Represents a booking made by a customer in the flight booking system.
    CommercialClassType
    Defines the different commercial class types available for flights.
    Customer
    Represents a customer in the flight booking system.
    Flight
    Represents a flight in the booking system, including its details, capacity, pricing, and passenger information.
    FlightBookingSystem
    Manages the operations of the flight booking system, including managing flights, customers, meals, and bookings.
    FlightType
    Defines the types of flights available in the system.
    Meal
    Represents a meal option available for selection on flights.
    MealType
    Defines the different types of meals available, primarily for dietary preferences.
    RebookFlight
    Command to rebook a flight within an existing booking.
